先解码header：eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9 = base64解码后是{"alg":"HS256","typ":"JWT"}

再解码payload：eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwiZXhwIjoxNzc1ODQxMTgxfQ = base64解码后是{"sub":"1","exp":1775841181}

